(217, 15, 'Meet Your Instructor', '<div class=\"_main--content-container--ILkoI\"><span><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h2 id=\"mehdi-razvi\">Mehdi Razvi</h2>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><div class=\"video-atom--video--1rflY\"><div aria-label=\"Loading…\" class=\"vds-loading vds-loading--md\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"vds-loading__children\"><div class=\"_1UN_ejel6QzQCa_M5Nn4bu\"><div class=\"_2lGVVA99VY-snhn6dzPP-z\"><div class=\"_3h3jXAJ1HmC2_sa49itKME _2nvHtsDYiD14gMJ8MpUp2c\"><div class=\"\"><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"1\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" id=\"widget2\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/k20ej-cQ5bk?showinfo=0&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;vq=hd720&amp;hl=en-us&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fclassroom.udacity.com&amp;widgetid=1\" title=\"ND063 C3 L0 01 Meet Your Instructor\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p>I have 17 years of  background as a developer, app support, DevOps, SRE, and as a consultant.  Most recently I have focused on cloud security and devops - primarily using Amazon Web Services.</p>\n<p>I\'m excited to share my knowledge and experience with you during this course!</p>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div></span></div>'),
(218, 15, 'Prerequisites', '<div class=\"_main--content-container--ILkoI\"><span><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h2 id=\"prerequisites\">Prerequisites</h2>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><div class=\"video-atom--video--1rflY\"><div aria-label=\"Loading…\" class=\"vds-loading vds-loading--md\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"vds-loading__children\"><div class=\"_1UN_ejel6QzQCa_M5Nn4bu\"><div class=\"_2lGVVA99VY-snhn6dzPP-z\"><div class=\"_3h3jXAJ1HmC2_sa49itKME _2nvHtsDYiD14gMJ8MpUp2c\"><div class=\"\"><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"1\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" id=\"widget2\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cDbjglTnjx4?showinfo=0&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;vq=hd720&amp;hl=en-us&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fclassroom.udacity.com&amp;widgetid=1\" title=\"ND063 C3 L0 02 Prerequisites\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h3 id=\"you-should-have-\">You Should Have...</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Completion of previous courses in the Cloud Architect Nanodegree program.</li>\n<li>Familiarity with web application architecture and infrastructure.</li>\n<li>Exposure to AWS console or CLI and basic compute services.</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div></span></div>'),
(219, 15, 'Introduction', '<div class=\"_main--content-container--ILkoI\"><span><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h2 id=\"designing-for-security\">Designing for Security</h2>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><div class=\"video-atom--video--1rflY\"><div aria-label=\"Loading…\" class=\"vds-loading vds-loading--md\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"vds-loading__children\"><div class=\"_1UN_ejel6QzQCa_M5Nn4bu\"><div class=\"_2lGVVA99VY-snhn6dzPP-z\"><div class=\"_3h3jXAJ1HmC2_sa49itKME _2nvHtsDYiD14gMJ8MpUp2c\"><div class=\"\"><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"1\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" id=\"widget2\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4rrNyGSzNbs?showinfo=0&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;vq=hd720&amp;hl=en-us&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fclassroom.udacity.com&amp;widgetid=1\" title=\"ND063 C3 L0 03 Introduction To Designing For Security\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p>In the cloud, the <strong>provider</strong> and the <strong>customer</strong> have different sets of responsibilities. These are laid out in what is called the <strong>Shared Responsibility Model</strong>.</p>\n<p>You can explore more about how it applies <a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/compliance/shared-responsibility-model/\" target=\"_blank\">when working in AWS here</a>.</p>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><div class=\"container--3sWx1\"><div class=\"prompt--1YMnx\"><h3 class=\"question-number--3IlDk\">Quiz Question</h3><div class=\"index-module--markdown--2MdcR ureact-markdown\"><p>Based on your new knowledge about the <strong>Shared Security Model</strong>, match who is responsible for what when working with cloud security.</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"index--answer-choices--2ziSF\"><div aria-dropeffect=\"move\" aria-label=\"Answer choice selections - tab through answer choices to match to concepts below.\" class=\"drop-zone--drop-zone--38cMu\" role=\"listbox\" tabindex=\"0\"><h3>Submit to check your answer choices!</h3></div></div><div class=\"index--labels--tWrVZ\"><h3><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p>Who</p>\n</div></h3><h3><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p>What</p>\n</div></h3></div><div class=\"index--answer-selections--3mNdz\"><div class=\"index--pair--2zqTz\"><div class=\"index--concept--AV9z3 index--pair-part--1zw9K\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p>Customer</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"index--answer-selection--bwGz3 index--pair-part--1zw9K\"><div aria-dropeffect=\"move\" aria-label=\"Customer - currently Responsibility *in* the Cloud\" class=\"drop-zone--drop-zone--38cMu\" role=\"listbox\" tabindex=\"0\"><div aria-label=\"Answer 1, Responsibility *in* the Cloud.\" class=\"drag-item--drag-item--3sB2T\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p>Responsibility <em>in</em> the Cloud</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"index--pair--2zqTz\"><div class=\"index--concept--AV9z3 index--pair-part--1zw9K\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p>Provider</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"index--answer-selection--bwGz3 index--pair-part--1zw9K\"><div aria-dropeffect=\"move\" aria-label=\"Provider - currently Responsibility *of* the Cloud\" class=\"drop-zone--drop-zone--38cMu\" role=\"listbox\" tabindex=\"0\"><div aria-label=\"Answer 1, Responsibility *of* the Cloud.\" class=\"drag-item--drag-item--3sB2T\" draggable=\"true\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p>Responsibility <em>of</em> the Cloud</p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"index--buttons--2-6jY _quiz-atom--buttons--3vJgG\"><button class=\"vds-button vds-button--primary\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"vds-button__content\">Submit</span></button></div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div></span></div>'),
(220, 15, 'Security Is Important', '<div class=\"_main--content-container--ILkoI\"><span><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h2 id=\"designing-for-security-is-important\">Designing for Security is Important</h2>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><div class=\"video-atom--video--1rflY\"><div aria-label=\"Loading…\" class=\"vds-loading vds-loading--md\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"vds-loading__children\"><div class=\"_1UN_ejel6QzQCa_M5Nn4bu\"><div class=\"_2lGVVA99VY-snhn6dzPP-z\"><div class=\"_3h3jXAJ1HmC2_sa49itKME _2nvHtsDYiD14gMJ8MpUp2c\"><div class=\"\"><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"1\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" id=\"widget2\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nj6TvlxRCac?showinfo=0&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;vq=hd720&amp;hl=en-us&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fclassroom.udacity.com&amp;widgetid=1\" title=\"ND063 C3 L0 04 Designing For Security Is Important\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p>In the video, we briefly touched on the expense and impact of cloud breaches. You can explore <a href=\"https://newsroom.ibm.com/2019-07-23-IBM-Study-Shows-Data-Breach-Costs-on-the-Rise-Financial-Impact-Felt-for-Years#assets_all\" target=\"_blank\">more of the data we talked about here</a>.</p>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div></span></div>'),
(221, 15, 'Business Stakeholders', '<div class=\"_main--content-container--ILkoI\"><span><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h2 id=\"business-stakeholders\">Business Stakeholders</h2>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><div class=\"video-atom--video--1rflY\"><div aria-label=\"Loading…\" class=\"vds-loading vds-loading--md\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"vds-loading__children\"><div class=\"_1UN_ejel6QzQCa_M5Nn4bu\"><div class=\"_2lGVVA99VY-snhn6dzPP-z\"><div class=\"_3h3jXAJ1HmC2_sa49itKME _2nvHtsDYiD14gMJ8MpUp2c\"><div class=\"\"><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"1\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" id=\"widget2\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HwS--ycmVFQ?showinfo=0&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;vq=hd720&amp;hl=en-us&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fclassroom.udacity.com&amp;widgetid=1\" title=\"ND063 C3 L0 05 Business Stakeholders\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h3 id=\"developers-and-enterprise-architects\">Developers and Enterprise Architects</h3>\n<p>Ensure cloud services they use are designed and developed with security in mind.</p>\n<h3 id=\"devops-and-sre-teams\">DevOps and SRE Teams</h3>\n<p>Ensure security is introduced ealy on and that cloud environments remain secure post-production.</p>\n<h3 id=\"infosec-teams\">InfoSec Teams</h3>\n<p>Secure systems and also benefit from being aware of security capabilities and architecture.</p>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div></span></div>'),
(222, 15, 'History of Security', '<div class=\"_main--content-container--ILkoI\"><span><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h2 id=\"history-of-designing-for-security\">History of Designing for Security</h2>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><div class=\"video-atom--video--1rflY\"><div aria-label=\"Loading…\" class=\"vds-loading vds-loading--md\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"vds-loading__children\"><div class=\"_1UN_ejel6QzQCa_M5Nn4bu\"><div class=\"_2lGVVA99VY-snhn6dzPP-z\"><div class=\"_3h3jXAJ1HmC2_sa49itKME _2nvHtsDYiD14gMJ8MpUp2c\"><div class=\"\"><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"1\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" id=\"widget2\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/fuaTioaw5vs?showinfo=0&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;vq=hd720&amp;hl=en-us&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fclassroom.udacity.com&amp;widgetid=1\" title=\"ND063 C3 L0 06 Quick History Of Designing For Security\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h2 id=\"security-in-the-cloud-a-little-history\">Security in the Cloud - A Little History</h2>\n<p>In the recent past, companies and governments have adopted the cloud at a lightning fast pace.</p>\n<p>The past few years have seen massive migrations of workloads into the public cloud and data centers are being closed and vacated right and left.</p>\n<p>Many organizations have a \"cloud first\" mandate in place for all new applications.</p>\n<p>With the rapid adoption of the cloud, we are also seeing a rise in cloud-related security breaches.</p>\n<p>Well known brands such as Facebook, Instagram, Accenture, Verizon, and CapitalOne are just a few companies that have been affected in the last few years. The impact can be huge in dollars, impact to users, and public image. </p>\n<p>Many of these breaches were a result of weak practices around designing and configuring cloud environments. In most cases, the root cause was simple misconfiguration of cloud storage or servers, which could have been easily prevented.</p>\n<p>In this course we will introduce you to best practices to prevent these misconfigurations and reduce the risk of a breach.</p>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div></span></div>'),
(223, 15, 'Course Outline', '<div class=\"_main--content-container--ILkoI\"><span><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h2 id=\"course-outline\">Course Outline</h2>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><div class=\"video-atom--video--1rflY\"><div aria-label=\"Loading…\" class=\"vds-loading vds-loading--md\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"vds-loading__children\"><div class=\"_1UN_ejel6QzQCa_M5Nn4bu\"><div class=\"_2lGVVA99VY-snhn6dzPP-z\"><div class=\"_3h3jXAJ1HmC2_sa49itKME _2nvHtsDYiD14gMJ8MpUp2c\"><div class=\"\"><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"1\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" id=\"widget2\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/6N2MEzxfT7k?showinfo=0&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;vq=hd720&amp;hl=en-us&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fclassroom.udacity.com&amp;widgetid=1\" title=\"ND063 C3 L0 07 Course Outline\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><span></span><div aria-label=\"Show Image Fullscreen\" class=\"image-atom--image-atom--1XDdu\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"image-atom-content--CDPca\"><div class=\"image-and-annotations-container--1U01s\"><img alt=\"A list of the lessons in this course.\" class=\"image--26lOQ\" src=\"https://video.udacity-data.com/topher/2020/April/5e94e8d7_screen-shot-2020-04-02-at-3.30.23-pm/screen-shot-2020-04-02-at-3.30.23-pm.png\" width=\"1394px\"/></div><div class=\"caption--2IK-Y\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p><strong>Your Path for Designing for Security</strong></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h3 id=\"course-outline\">Course Outline</h3>\n<p>This course focuses on architectural best practices around cloud security.</p>\n<h4 id=\"identity-and-access-management\">Identity and Access Management</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>We will start with looking at identity and access management in AWS. </li>\n<li>You will learn to secure users and roles who manage and control resources in the cloud. </li>\n<li>We will also investigate best practices around authentication, authorization and fine tuning user permissions.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"securing-access-to-cloud-infrastructure\">Securing Access to Cloud Infrastructure</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>We will also explore methods to ensure cloud infrastructure and networks are protected from unauthorized access. </li>\n<li>This will include techniques to secure and harden access to instances and servers. </li>\n<li>Additionally, we will delve into network controls offered by the cloud provider. </li>\n<li>You will also get an overview of various methods to securely connect to cloud networks.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"data-protection-in-the-cloud\">Data Protection in the Cloud</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>We will cover techniques and methods related to protecting data stored in the cloud. </li>\n<li>We will leverage encryption capabilities offered by AWS. </li>\n<li>Finally, we will demonstrate best practices for encryption key management.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"defensive-security-in-the-cloud\">Defensive Security in the Cloud</h3>\n<p>We will tie this all together by looking at how to incorporate security in your cloud operational model. </p>\n<ul>\n<li>We will monitor systems to discover risks early on.</li>\n<li>We will use tools to discover vulnerabilities and insecure configurations.</li>\n<li>We will also review some of the AWS cloud services which can defend web applications from external threats.</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div></span></div>');
INSERT INTO `chapitre` (`id_chapitre`, `id_lesson`, `nom_chapitre`, `HTML`) VALUES
(224, 15, 'Tools & Dependencies', '<div class=\"_main--content-container--ILkoI\"><span><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div class=\"ltr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><h2 id=\"tools-environment-dependencies\">Tools, Environment &amp; Dependencies</h2>\n</div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><div class=\"video-atom--video--1rflY\"><div aria-label=\"Loading…\" class=\"vds-loading vds-loading--md\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"vds-loading__children\"><div class=\"_1UN_ejel6QzQCa_M5Nn4bu\"><div class=\"_2lGVVA99VY-snhn6dzPP-z\"><div class=\"_3h3jXAJ1HmC2_sa49itKME _2nvHtsDYiD14gMJ8MpUp2c\"><div class=\"\"><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"1\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" id=\"widget2\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xxhZMuJ4NKE?showinfo=0&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;vq=hd720&amp;hl=en-us&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fclassroom.udacity.com&amp;widgetid=1\" title=\"ND063 C3 L0 08 Tools, Environment &amp; Dependencies\" width=\"640\"></iframe></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><span></span></div><span></span></div></div><div><div class=\"index--container--2OwOl\"><div class=\"index--atom--lmAIo layout--content--3Smmq\"><div><div class=\"task-list-atom--container--WBrU5\"><header class=\"task-list-atom--header--3bRGC\"><h3 class=\"task-list-atom--title--1bHiw\">Tools, Environment &amp; Dependencies Checklist</h3><h5 class=\"task-list-atom--description--1K-fr\"><div class=\"_15vzQlp3FJ8f94suLiPCPf ureact-markdown\"><p>Make sure you have all of the following:</p>\n</div></h5></header><div class=\"task-list-atom--tasks-container--3MvCe\"><span class=\"task-list-atom--icon-container--3-v6v\">Task List</span><ul class=